Task is a program that helps you keep track of what you are doing.

Task will ask you what you are doing. If you need to change tasks you type "n"
It will then ask you what the new task is. If you want to enter any information
about the task you are working on type the letter "i". Task will then ask
what the information is and store it with the current task. When you have completed
a task type "c". Task will confirm and then show you the next task you need to completed

